<node CREATED="1576216631221" ID="ID_477148006" MODIFIED="1576216631221" TEXT="Atom Publishing Protocol which simplifies blog publishing is a(n) _____ application. representational state transfer _____ uses simpler structures than SOAP protocols often including an XML- or XHTML-tagged data set to implement Web services." />
