<node CREATED="1576216631227" ID="ID_49779473" MODIFIED="1576216631227" TEXT="Before you can upload data to Amazon S3 you must create a bucket in one of the AWS Regions to store your data in. After you create a bucket you can upload an unlimited number of data objects to the bucket. A bucket is owned by the AWS account that created it. By default you can create up to 100 buckets in each of your AWS accounts. " />
