<node CREATED="1576216631228" ID="ID_1806927606" MODIFIED="1576216631228" TEXT="Elastic Load Balancing supports the following types of load balancers: Application Load Balancers Network Load Balancers and Classic Load Balancers. Amazon ECS services can use either type of load balancer. Application Load Balancers are used to route HTTP/HTTPS (or Layer 7) traffic. Network Load Balancers and Classic Load Balancers are used to route TCP (or Layer 4) traffic." />
